# Deep zoom perturbation experiment
prototype/deep-zoom/

# Palette library — baked by `npm run bake:palette` from H:/GMT/stuff/palette-lab
# (NOT in this repo, so a clean checkout / CI cannot regenerate these).
#  • core.*       = TRACKED — clean, redistributable (MIT/Apache/BSD/CC0), ~0.5 MB. Ships always.
#  • softology.*  = ignored — provenance-unverified aggregate. Lazy-loaded; serve from R2 or omit.
#  • cptcity.*    = ignored — per-collection redistribution-bound. Lazy-loaded; serve from R2 or omit.
public/palette/softology.bin.gz
public/palette/softology.json.gz
public/palette/cptcity.bin.gz
public/palette/cptcity.json.gz

